{"type": "article", "id": 52013, "title": "在拥挤的地铁上怎么看书？这个小工具帮你｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-04-10T23:20:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 44125, "name": "Klipy Design"}, {"id": 42950, "name": "IA Collaborative"}, {"id": 33904, "name": "Foscarini"}, {"id": 49169, "name": "Maruni"}, {"id": 49170, "name": "Francisco Abarca"}, {"id": 49171, "name": "Robert Sukrachand"}, {"id": 49172, "name": "Ignacio Merino"}, {"id": 939, "name": "Jasper Morrison"}, {"id": 28545, "name": "Naoto Fukasawa"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 25, "praise_count": 153, "image": "img/article/article_show/201804102109367c9ITHX6WtrjPO1N.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Roundish &amp; Fugu by Naoto Fukasawa &amp; Jasper Morrison for Maruni</h3><p>“工艺品工业化”是日本家具品牌 Maruni 一直以来的品牌精神，自 1928 年成立于广岛以来，创造了许多高品质的木制家具。最近，它将推出两款由深泽直人和英国极简主义大师 Jasper Morrison 设计的“舒适”木椅。</p><p>深泽直人设计的 Roundish 扶手椅由单件层压胶合板制成，他解释说：“坐着的时候，感觉很舒服，就像人的身体被舒适地包裹起来一样，无论是作为休闲椅还是餐椅，它都能提供温柔、轻松的时光。”</p><p>而从 2011 年与 Maruni 合作的 Jasper Morrison，设计了一把名为 Fugu 的椅子，采用坚固的橡木制成，采用 Maruni 的精密切割技术制成的轻微弯曲的座椅和靠背。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211017Fk4eUjJBMXo1xyuN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804102110205yBvz84buE3mpdwC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.999577\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211021T5JFOwyt2jqVaKeH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211022Of3cHiF9vyXn5Rzs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211022zimTdS4MgLWrC6af.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/04/08/jasper-morrison-naoto-fukasawa-maruni-milan-design-week/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Morsetto Lamps by Foscarini + Ignacio Merino</h3><p>意大利照明设计品牌 Foscarini 与瑞士洛桑艺术设计大学的学生 Ignacio Merino 合作，设计了 Morsetto 系列灯具，由丙烯酸制成，看起来像是牙膏管的一部分。</p><p>这是一系列可充电的无线灯具，需要将丙烯酸管加热到 300℃，再凹成需要的造型，看起来是一组很具有实验性质的作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=v0626w6b4lr&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018041021110195wAnaoOMI8r4Eh2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211101K6a1khAr5L9BuYp4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211101vXJPDbgaz4781cUe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211102AOp2PjbclviZBnsI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211102DXl9ChymivFJGMTa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211102ZfMazYGUpCLPJDQO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/foscarini-ignacio-merino-morsetto-lamps-toothpaste-tubes-04-09-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Torus Collection &amp; Cyc Mirror by Robert Sukrachand</h3><p>在最近的 Architectural Digest 设计展上，设计师 Robert Sukrachand 推出了两个新系列，其一是 Torus 系列，包括以微型装饰为特色的桌子和搁板，其二是由青铜镜和弯曲玻璃制成的 Cyc 镜子。这两个系列都融合了戏剧性的曲线和轮廓。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211230qxMzBl5JThbmUAc2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211231qol3kf6YTPnG28i0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211231YGmaLflhM6oScR9E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211231oeN9FJbKtHlfn8dw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804102112312YRpPj0QMTi9gqmG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211232r0hsyuLlOQ6ZbocB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211232fTptB87uyXzixjZC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Design Milk<h3><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 54, 54); font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">Kelvin Home Coffee Roaster by IA Collaborative</span></h3></figcaption></figure></div><p>设计团队 IA Collaborative 最近在众筹网站 Kickstarter 上推出了一款 Kelvin 家庭咖啡烘焙机。团队的灵感来源于观察咖啡文化，意识到人们会竭尽全力获得最纯粹的家用咖啡体验——甚至使用家庭爆米花机和笨重、昂贵的商业级烘焙机。</p><p>所有细节的设计都考虑到了用户体验：耐用的优质材料，干净、优雅和低调的轮廓，自豪地展示或折叠存储，以及简化的控制机制，仅有一个简单的旋钮，控制所有程序。</p><p>Kelvin 先后拿下了 iF 设计奖，IDEA 设计奖和美国 Good Design 奖项。售价 229 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/iacollaborative/kelvin-home-coffee-roaster?ref=blxi8f\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211752ef5pZ4knQvgaWF81.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563063\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211754I0hJMT8DjKpQE75f.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560669\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211316JWPZoOCEHtim4FLa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.375238\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211316vrQRCFzPq4HVoAj0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211316fBqF8ATeyxr1uUQN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211316gtDyA0x3rJjLi5zE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804102113163qDoPaixJWORyF75.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/04/09/roasting-your-coffee-is-a-beautiful-tasty-act-of-rebellion/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>LECTOR by Francisco Abarca</h3><p>在地铁或巴士之类的公共交通工具上看书，尤其是在人多嘈杂拥挤的时候，确实是个难题。设计师 Francisco Abarca 提出了一种解决方案。这是一个名为 LECTOR 的小配件，便于用户单手握住一本书，解放另一只手去抓扶手。</p><p>符合人体工程学的驱动形状有助于握持，并且可以形成舒适的姿势，确保长时间使用后不会感到不适。LECTORS 使用 3D 打印技术制作而成，且足够小巧，便于随身携带。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211430WlNXET7f9Ran0cxj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211430hbHIuAXfaKRgvW3Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211431IFXVwZtaJgifBl20.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211431NMfynE7x5wm1hGHL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/04/08/reading-on-the-move/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Cake Divider by Klipy Design</h3><p>为了帮助人们均分食物，Klipy Design 推出了一款带刻度的辅助工具。只要将它插在披萨或是蛋糕正中央，转到对应的人数，比如 6、8、10 和 14 人四种设置，再用刀沿着指引槽切开即可。这个方便的小工具可以根据你需要的切片的数量来设定切割蛋糕或是披萨的角度和厚度。售价 105.57 元，<a href=\"https://www.amazon.cn/gp/product/B009MTT6R8/ref=ox_sc_act_title_1?tag=geo-23&amp;smid=A28ACMVQIZOEMD&amp;psc=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211548KkahiW7jqlIfJg0c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180410211548gk5GKQd1HUy0StmE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804102115486GociKFJnTRDYXAz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804102115483bBIxFLMfKd5CrXu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804102115489WxBSuqMIsP8Ykiz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}